shard-manifest
Copyright 2026 Lightweb Inc. (https://lightweb.net)

=========================================================================

This software is a small standalone daemon that periodically emits BRC-137
ShardManifest datagrams to the IPv6 multicast beacon group, advertising
the local participant's shard_bits configuration and the set of shard
groups it has joined. It is intended for use alongside shard-proxy,
shard-listener, and retry-endpoint to give operators on-network
visibility into the sharding configuration of every participant and a
hook for future automated coordination.

