Third-Party Standards

This software implements BRC-137: Shard Manifest Announcement, a
companion specification to the BSV multicast transaction distribution
stack. Wire-frame magic and protocol version constants are inherited
from BRC-12 and BRC-124, published standards maintained by BSV
Blockchain:

  BRC-12: Raw Transaction Format
  BRC-124: Multicast Frame Format
  BSV Blockchain Standards Repository
  https://github.com/bitcoin-sv/BRCs/

